#: templates/base/layout.html:13
msgid "Zero-knowledge secret sharing"
msgstr "Intet kendskab hemmeligheds deling"

#: templates/base/layout.html:27 templates/whispers/about.html:4
msgid "About"
msgstr "Om"

#: templates/base/layout.html:47
msgid "Sign out"
msgstr "Log ud"

#: templates/base/layout.html:64
msgid "Your whisper is safe with us."
msgstr "Din whisper er sikker hos os."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:9
msgid "About psst-secret"
msgstr "Om psst-secret"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:10
msgid ""
"A privacy focused app for sharing secrets securely. We call them whispers."
msgstr ""
"En privatlivsfokuseret app til at dele hemmeligheder sikkert. Vi kalder dem "
"whispers."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:15
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "Sådan virker det"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:17
msgid ""
"psst-secret ensures that <strong class=\"text-white\">your whispers never "
"exist in plaintext on our server</strong>. All encryption and decryption "
"happens entirely in your browser using the <a href=\"https://developer."
"mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\" class=\"text-brand-400 "
"underline hover:text-brand-300\" target=\"_blank\">Web Crypto API</a>."
msgstr ""
"psst-secret sikrer, at <strong class=\"text-white\">dine whispers aldrig "
"findes i klartekst på vores server</strong>. Al kryptering og dekryptering "
"foregår udelukkende i din browser ved hjælp af <a href=\"https://developer."
"mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\" class=\"text-brand-400 "
"underline hover:text-brand-300\" target=\"_blank\">Web Crypto API</a>."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:21
msgid "Creating a Whisper"
msgstr "Opret en whisper"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:23
msgid "You type your whisper in the browser"
msgstr "Du skriver din whisper i browseren"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:24
msgid ""
"A random <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">AES-256-GCM</strong> key is "
"generated client-side"
msgstr ""
"En tilfældig <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">AES-256-GCM</strong>-nøgle "
"genereres på klientsiden"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:25
msgid "Your whisper is encrypted in-browser"
msgstr "Din whisper krypteres i browseren"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:26
msgid "Only the <em>ciphertext</em> is sent to the server"
msgstr "Kun <em>ciphertext</em> sendes til serveren"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:27
msgid ""
"The decryption key is placed in the URL fragment (<code class=\"text-"
"brand-300\">#key</code>)"
msgstr ""
"Dekrypteringsnøglen placeres i URL-fragmentet (<code class=\"text-"
"brand-300\">#key</code>)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:31
msgid "Viewing a Whisper"
msgstr "Se en whisper"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:33
msgid "You open the shared link"
msgstr "Du åbner det delte link"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:34
msgid "The server returns the ciphertext"
msgstr "Serveren returnerer ciphertext"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:35
msgid "The key from the URL fragment decrypts it in-browser"
msgstr "Nøglen fra URL-fragmentet dekrypterer den i browseren"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:36
msgid "You see the plaintext — the server never does"
msgstr "Du ser klartekst — det gør serveren aldrig"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:45
msgid "Why the URL Fragment?"
msgstr "Hvorfor URL-fragmentet?"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:47
msgid ""
"The decryption key is stored after the <code class='bg-gray-900 px-1.5 "
"py-0.5 rounded text-brand-300'>#</code> in the URL. Per the HTTP "
"specification, <strong class='text-white'>the URL fragment is never sent to "
"the server</strong> — it's processed only by the browser. This means:"
msgstr ""
"Dekrypteringsnøglen gemmes efter <code class='bg-gray-900 px-1.5 py-0.5 "
"rounded text-brand-300'>#</code> i URL'en. Ifølge HTTP-specifikationen "
"<strong class='text-white'>sendes URL-fragmentet aldrig til serveren</"
"strong> — det behandles kun af browseren. Det betyder:"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:49
msgid "The server never receives the decryption key"
msgstr "Serveren modtager aldrig dekrypteringsnøglen"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:50
msgid "The key doesn't appear in server logs or analytics"
msgstr "Nøglen fremgår ikke af serverlogs eller analyseværktøjer"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:51
msgid "Even if the server is compromised, your whispers remain encrypted"
msgstr "Selv hvis serveren kompromitteres, forbliver dine whispers krypterede"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:58
msgid "Password Protection"
msgstr "Adgangskodebeskyttelse"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:60
msgid ""
"Optionally, you can set a password when creating a whisper. When a password "
"is used:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan valgfrit angive en adgangskode, når du opretter en whisper. Når der "
"bruges en adgangskode:"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:62
msgid ""
"The encryption key is derived from your password using <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-200\">PBKDF2</strong> (600,000 iterations, SHA-256)"
msgstr ""
"Krypteringsnøglen udledes af din adgangskode ved hjælp af <strong "
"class=\"text-gray-200\">PBKDF2</strong> (600.000 iterationer, SHA-256)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:63
msgid ""
"A random <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">salt</strong> is generated and "
"stored on the server (useless without the password)"
msgstr ""
"Der genereres en tilfældig <strong class=\"text-gray-200\">salt</strong>, "
"som gemmes på serveren (ubrugelig uden adgangskoden)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:64
msgid ""
"The URL contains <em>no key fragment</em> — only the password holder can "
"decrypt"
msgstr ""
"URL'en indeholder <em>intet nøglefragment</em> — kun den, der kender "
"adgangskoden, kan dekryptere"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:65
msgid "This provides an extra layer of security for highly sensitive data"
msgstr "Det giver et ekstra sikkerhedslag til meget følsomme data"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:72
msgid "Security Features"
msgstr "Sikkerhedsfunktioner"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:75
msgid "Burn After Reading"
msgstr "Slet efter læsning"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:76
msgid ""
"Whispers marked as burn-after-read are <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanently erased from memory</strong> the moment they are "
"viewed — not just flagged, but gone."
msgstr ""
"Whispers markeret til sletning efter læsning bliver <strong class=\"text-"
"gray-300\">permanent slettet fra hukommelsen</strong> i det øjeblik, de "
"bliver vist — ikke bare markeret, men væk."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:79
msgid "Auto-Expiry"
msgstr "Automatisk udløb"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:80
msgid ""
"All whispers require an expiration time (5 minutes to 1 month). Expired "
"whispers are automatically evicted from Redis via TTL and continuously "
"purged by a background process."
msgstr ""
"Alle whispers kræver en udløbstid (5 minutter til 1 måned). Udløbne whispers "
"fjernes automatisk fra Redis via TTL og ryddes løbende af en baggrundsproces."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:84
msgid ""
"Industry-standard authenticated encryption. Provides both confidentiality "
"and integrity — any tampering with the ciphertext is detected."
msgstr ""
"Industristandard autentificeret kryptering. Giver både fortrolighed og "
"integritet — enhver manipulering af ciphertext opdages."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:87
msgid "Zero Knowledge"
msgstr "Intet kendskab"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:88
msgid ""
"The server stores only ciphertext, IV, and optional salt — and only in "
"volatile memory (Redis). It has no ability to decrypt your data, even under "
"compulsion."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer kun ciphertext, IV og eventuel salt — og kun i flygtig "
"hukommelse (Redis). Den har ingen mulighed for at dekryptere dine data, selv "
"under tvang."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:95
msgid "What the Server Stores"
msgstr "Hvad serveren gemmer"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:98
msgid "Redis (in-memory only — never touches disk)"
msgstr "Redis (kun i hukommelsen — skriver aldrig til disk)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:102 templates/whispers/about.html:118
msgid "Field"
msgstr "Felt"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:103 templates/whispers/about.html:119
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Formål"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:107
msgid "Your encrypted data (useless without the key)"
msgstr "Dine krypterede data (ubrugelige uden nøglen)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:108
msgid "Random initialization vector for AES-GCM"
msgstr "Tilfældig initialiseringsvektor til AES-GCM"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:109
msgid "PBKDF2 salt (only if password-protected)"
msgstr "PBKDF2-salt (kun hvis adgangskodebeskyttet)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:114
msgid "PostgreSQL (metadata only)"
msgstr "PostgreSQL (kun metadata)"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:123
msgid "When the whisper will be auto-deleted"
msgstr "Hvornår whisperen slettes automatisk"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:124
msgid "Whether to delete on first view"
msgstr "Om den skal slettes ved første visning"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:125
msgid "Send or receive"
msgstr "Send eller modtag"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:126
msgid "IP/CIDR restriction"
msgstr "IP/CIDR-begrænsning"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:130
msgid ""
"The server does <strong>not</strong> store: plaintext, encryption keys, "
"passwords, or any identifying information. Encrypted data lives only in "
"volatile memory and is lost if Redis restarts."
msgstr ""
"Serveren gemmer <strong>ikke</strong>: klartekst, krypteringsnøgler, "
"adgangskoder eller identificerende oplysninger. Krypterede data findes kun i "
"flygtig hukommelse og går tabt, hvis Redis genstarter."

#: templates/whispers/about.html:136
msgid "Tech Stack"
msgstr "Teknologistak"

#: templates/whispers/about.html:150
msgid "Create a whisper"
msgstr "Opret en whisper"

#: templates/whispers/burned.html:4
msgid "Whisper Burned"
msgstr "Whisper brændt"

#: templates/whispers/burned.html:9
msgid "This whisper has been burned"
msgstr "Denne whisper er brændt"

#: templates/whispers/burned.html:10
msgid ""
"This was a burn-after-reading whisper and has already been viewed. It no "
"longer exists."
msgstr ""
"Dette var en whisper med sletning efter læsning og den er allerede blevet "
"vist. Den findes ikke længere."

#: templates/whispers/burned.html:12 templates/whispers/expired.html:12
msgid "Create a new whisper"
msgstr "Opret en ny whisper"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:4
msgid "New Whisper"
msgstr "Ny whisper"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:9
msgid "Share a whisper"
msgstr "Del en whisper"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:10
msgid ""
"Your content is encrypted in your browser before it reaches our server. We "
"never see your plaintext."
msgstr ""
"Dit indhold krypteres i din browser, før det når vores server. Vi ser aldrig "
"din klartekst."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:17
msgid "Send"
msgstr "Send"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:21
msgid "Receive"
msgstr "Modtag"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:30 templates/whispers/submit.html:18
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Tekst"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:34 templates/whispers/submit.html:22
msgid "File"
msgstr "Fil"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:40 templates/whispers/submit.html:28
msgid "Whisper content"
msgstr "Whisper-indhold"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:43
msgid "Type your whisper here…"
msgstr "Skriv din whisper her…"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:48 templates/whispers/submit.html:36
msgid "Whisper file"
msgstr "Whisper-fil"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:55 templates/whispers/submit.html:43
msgid "Click to select a file or drag & drop"
msgstr "Klik for at vælge en fil eller træk og slip"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:56 templates/whispers/submit.html:44
msgid "Any file type supported."
msgstr "Alle filtyper understøttes."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:56 templates/whispers/submit.html:44
#, python-format
msgid "Max upload size: %(max_size)s"
msgstr "Maks. uploadstørrelse: %(max_size)s"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:62 templates/whispers/submit.html:50
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Fjern"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:69
msgid "Receive mode"
msgstr "Modtag-tilstand"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:69
msgid "create a request for someone to send you a whisper."
msgstr "opret en forespørgsel, så nogen kan sende dig en whisper."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:70
msgid ""
"You'll get two links: a <strong>submit link</strong> to share with the "
"sender, and a <strong>view link</strong> for you to retrieve the whisper "
"once it's been submitted."
msgstr ""
"Du får to links: et <strong>indsend-link</strong> til at dele med afsenderen "
"og et <strong>visningslink</strong> til at hente whisperen, når den er "
"blevet indsendt."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:77
msgid "Expires after"
msgstr "Udløber efter"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:80
msgid "5 Minutes"
msgstr "5 minutter"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:81
msgid "1 Hour"
msgstr "1 time"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:82
msgid "1 Day"
msgstr "1 dag"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:83
msgid "1 Week"
msgstr "1 uge"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:84
msgid "1 Month"
msgstr "1 måned"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:93
msgid "Burn after reading"
msgstr "Slet efter læsning"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:97
msgid ""
"When enabled, the whisper will be permanently deleted after being viewed "
"once. The recipient gets one chance to see it."
msgstr ""
"Når det er aktiveret, slettes whisperen permanent efter at være blevet vist "
"én gang. Modtageren får én chance for at se den."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:105
msgid "Encrypt & Share"
msgstr "Krypter og del"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:108
msgid "Create Request"
msgstr "Opret forespørgsel"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:115
msgid "Advanced Options"
msgstr "Avancerede indstillinger"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:120 templates/whispers/login.html:38
#: templates/whispers/submit.html:58
msgid "Password"
msgstr "Adgangskode"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:121 templates/whispers/create.html:131
msgid "optional"
msgstr "valgfrit"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:125
msgid "Extra protection…"
msgstr "Ekstra beskyttelse…"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:126
msgid ""
"Adds an extra layer of encryption. The recipient will need this password in "
"addition to the link to decrypt the psst."
msgstr ""
"Tilføjer et ekstra lag kryptering. Modtageren skal bruge denne adgangskode "
"ud over linket for at dekryptere en whisper."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:130
msgid "Restrict by IP"
msgstr "Begræns efter IP"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:135
msgid "e.g. 203.0.113.5 or 10.0.0.0/24"
msgstr "fx 203.0.113.5 eller 10.0.0.0/24"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:136
msgid ""
"Only this IP/CIDR will be able to <strong>view</strong> the whisper. A bare "
"IP is treated as /32."
msgstr ""
"Kun denne IP/CIDR kan <strong>se</strong> whisperen. En enkelt IP behandles "
"som /32."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:137
msgid ""
"Only this IP/CIDR will be able to <strong>submit</strong> a whisper. A bare "
"IP is treated as /32."
msgstr ""
"Kun denne IP/CIDR kan <strong>indsende</strong> en whisper. En enkelt IP "
"behandles som /32."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:144
msgid "Require authentication to view"
msgstr "Kræv autentificering for at se"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:148
msgid "The person viewing this whisper must be signed in."
msgstr "Personen der ser whisper skal være logget ind."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:156
msgid "Require authentication to submit"
msgstr "Kræv autentificering for at sende"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:160
msgid "The person submitting a whisper to this request must be signed in."
msgstr "Personen der sender en whisper skal være logget ind."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:174
msgid "Whisper created!"
msgstr "Whisper oprettet!"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:175
msgid ""
"Share this link. The decryption key is in the URL fragment and is "
"<strong>never sent to the server</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Del dette link. Dekrypteringsnøglen ligger i URL-fragmentet og bliver "
"<strong>aldrig sendt til serveren</strong>."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:181 templates/whispers/create.html:211
#: templates/whispers/create.html:222 templates/whispers/view.html:42
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopiér"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:185
msgid ""
"This whisper is password-protected. The recipient will need the password to "
"decrypt it."
msgstr ""
"Denne whisper er adgangskodebeskyttet. Modtageren skal bruge adgangskoden "
"for at dekryptere den."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:188
msgid "This whisper will be destroyed after being viewed once."
msgstr "Denne whisper bliver slettet, når den er blevet vist én gang."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:193 templates/whispers/create.html:237
msgid "Create another whisper"
msgstr "Opret en anden whisper"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:200
msgid "Request created!"
msgstr "Forespørgsel oprettet!"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:201
msgid ""
"Share the <strong>submit link</strong> with the person who should send you a "
"whisper. Use the <strong>view link</strong> to retrieve it once they've "
"submitted."
msgstr ""
"Del <strong>indsend-linket</strong> med personen, der skal sende dig en "
"whisper. Brug <strong>visningslinket</strong> til at hente den, når den er "
"blevet indsendt."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:205
msgid "Submit link — share this with the sender"
msgstr "Indsend-link — del dette med afsenderen"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:216
msgid "View link — for you to retrieve the whisper"
msgstr "Visningslink — til at hente whisperen"

#: templates/whispers/create.html:229
msgid ""
"This request is password-protected. Share the password separately with the "
"sender."
msgstr ""
"Denne forespørgsel er adgangskodebeskyttet. Del adgangskoden separat med "
"afsenderen."

#: templates/whispers/create.html:232
msgid "The whisper will be destroyed after you view it once."
msgstr "Whisperen bliver slettet, efter du har set den én gang."

#: templates/whispers/expired.html:4
msgid "Whisper Expired"
msgstr "Whisper udløbet"

#: templates/whispers/expired.html:9
msgid "This whisper has expired"
msgstr "Denne whisper er udløbet"

#: templates/whispers/expired.html:10
msgid ""
"The whisper you're looking for has passed its expiration time and has been "
"permanently deleted."
msgstr ""
"Whisperen, du leder efter, har overskredet sin udløbstid og er blevet "
"slettet permanent."

#: templates/whispers/forbidden.html:4
msgid "Access Denied"
msgstr "Adgang nægtet"

#: templates/whispers/forbidden.html:9
msgid "Access denied"
msgstr "Adgang nægtet"

#: templates/whispers/forbidden.html:10
msgid "Your IP address is not allowed to access this whisper."
msgstr "Din IP-adresse har ikke adgang til denne whisper."

#: templates/whispers/forbidden.html:12 templates/whispers/submitted.html:12
msgid "Create your own whisper"
msgstr "Opret din egen whisper"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:4 templates/whispers/login.html:45
msgid "Sign in"
msgstr "Login"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:17
msgid "Sign in to continue"
msgstr "Login for at fortsætte"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:32
msgid "Username"
msgstr ""

#: templates/whispers/login.html:35
msgid "Enter username…"
msgstr "Indtast brugernavn..."

#: templates/whispers/login.html:41 templates/whispers/view.html:15
msgid "Enter password…"
msgstr "Indtast adgangskode…"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:55
msgid "or"
msgstr "eller"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:65
msgid "Sign in with"
msgstr "Login med"

#: templates/whispers/login.html:72
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "No sign-in providers configured."
msgid "No sign-in methods configured."
msgstr "Ingen login ubydere konfigureret"

#: templates/whispers/pending.html:4
msgid "Waiting for Whisper"
msgstr "Venter på whisper"

#: templates/whispers/pending.html:9
msgid "Waiting for whisper…"
msgstr "Venter på whisper…"

#: templates/whispers/pending.html:10
msgid ""
"The whisper hasn't been submitted yet. This page will automatically refresh."
msgstr ""
"Whisperen er ikke blevet indsendt endnu. Denne side opdateres automatisk."

#: templates/whispers/pending.html:12
#, python-format
msgid "This request expires at %(expires_at)s."
msgstr "Denne forespørgsel udløber %(expires_at)s."

#: templates/whispers/pending.html:15
msgid "← Back to home"
msgstr "← Tilbage til forsiden"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:4 templates/whispers/submit.html:9
msgid "Submit a Whisper"
msgstr "Indsend en whisper"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:10
msgid ""
"Someone has requested you share a whisper with them. Your content is "
"encrypted in your browser before it reaches our server."
msgstr ""
"Nogen har bedt dig om at dele en whisper med dem. Dit indhold krypteres i "
"din browser, før det når vores server."

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:31
msgid "Enter the whisper here…"
msgstr "Skriv whisperen her…"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:58
msgid "required"
msgstr "påkrævet"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:61
msgid "Enter the password…"
msgstr "Indtast adgangskoden…"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:62
msgid ""
"The requester has set a password. You must enter it to encrypt your whisper."
msgstr ""
"Anmoderen har angivet en adgangskode. Du skal indtaste den for at kryptere "
"din whisper."

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:68
msgid ""
"This whisper will be destroyed after being viewed once by the requester."
msgstr ""
"Denne whisper bliver slettet, efter at den er blevet vist én gang af "
"anmoderen."

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:75
msgid "Encrypt & Submit"
msgstr "Krypter og indsend"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:83
msgid "Whisper submitted!"
msgstr "Whisper indsendt!"

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:84
msgid ""
"Your encrypted whisper has been submitted. The requester can now view it."
msgstr "Din krypterede whisper er blevet indsendt. Anmoderen kan nu se den."

#: templates/whispers/submit.html:87
msgid "← Create your own whisper"
msgstr "← Opret din egen whisper"

#: templates/whispers/submitted.html:4
msgid "Already Submitted"
msgstr "Allerede indsendt"

#: templates/whispers/submitted.html:9
msgid "Whisper already submitted"
msgstr "Whisper allerede indsendt"

#: templates/whispers/submitted.html:10
msgid ""
"A whisper has already been submitted for this request. Each request can only "
"receive one submission."
msgstr ""
